# Aaditri Emerland Community App

Mobile-first PWA for residents of Aaditri Emerland. See `AGENTS.md` for the full rulebook.

## Tech Stack

- **Next.js `16.2.4`** (App Router, Turbopack dev)
- **React `19.2.4`** + **TypeScript `^5`**
- **Tailwind CSS `^4`**
- **Supabase** (`@supabase/ssr`, `@supabase/supabase-js`) — Auth, Postgres, Storage, RLS
- **next-pwa** + `public/manifest.json`
- **lucide-react**, **react-hot-toast**, **date-fns**
- Hosted on **Vercel**

## Key Files

- `src/proxy.ts` — auth + role gating (runs before every request on `/dashboard/*` and `/admin/*`)
- `src/lib/supabase.ts` — browser client factory
- `src/lib/supabase-server.ts` — Server Component client factory
- `src/hooks/useAuth.ts` — client-side auth + profile hook with a `mounted` flag
- `src/types/index.ts` — shared types (`Profile`, `Announcement`, `Event`, `Booking`, …)
- `supabase/schema.sql` — tables, RLS policies, storage buckets

## Brand

- Primary color `#1B5E20` (dark green)
- Accent `#FFD700` (gold)
- Background `#F5F5F5`
